name: Felix Tagge
content:
Felix Tagge was a human male member of the House of Tagge who served as one of the Tagge Corporation's two Heads of Finance during the Galactic Civil War. The other Head of Finance was Adelaide Tagge, whom Felix referred to as "dear." Felix and Adelaide served on the Board of the Tagge Corporation, led by Adelaide's cousin Domina Tagge.
Felix Tagge first appeared via imagination in the fifth issue of the 2020 comic series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra . He first appeared in-person and was first identified in the 2021 comic War of the Bounty Hunters â€“ Boushh 1. Doctor Aphra  author Alyssa Wong has stated on Twitter that Felix and Adelaide Tagge were the parents of Ronen Tagge, though no canon source has confirmed this.
